  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Incorporated in 2015, Magenta Lifecare Limited manufactures mattresses and pillows. The company offers foam-based products under the brand \"Magenta\" in India.</p>\n<p>Magenta Lifecare's product portfolio includes memory foam, latex-based, bonded mattresses, pocketed springs etc. and pillows such as memory foam pillows, moulded memory foam pillows, moulded contour foam pillows etc.</p>\n<p>Magenta Lifecare Limited's manufacturing facility is located in Gujarat, India. The installed capacity for manufacturing mattresses is currently at 60,000 Nos. and 70,000 nos. of pillows.</p>\n<p>As of date of Prospectus, The company's overall staff strength is 41 employees. The products the company offers to the customers are spread across retail, hotels and institutions.</p>\n<p><strong>Competitive Strengths:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Diversified customer base and long-standing relationship with the customers.</li>\n<li>Extensive and well-developed pan-India sales and distribution network.</li>\n<li>Diversified Product portfolio.</li>\n<li>Experienced Promoter Directors with extensive domain knowledge.</li>\n<li>Quality assurance and accreditations.</li>\n</ul>"
  },
